<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="ms">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Kad Hari Raya</title>
<style>
    body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f9d58, #34a853);
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        height: 100vh;
        color: white;
    }.card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 30px;
    text-align: center;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in-out;
}

h1 {
    font-size: 2.5em;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

p {
    font-size: 1.2em;
}

.moon {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, #fff, #ddd);
    border-radius: 50%;
    position: relative;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
    box-shadow: -10px 0 0 0 #34a853;
}

.lantern {
    width: 10px;
    height: 40px;
    background: gold;
    margin: 10px auto;
    border-radius: 5px;
    animation: swing 2s infinite ease-in-out;
}

@keyframes swing {
    0% { transform: rotate(5deg); }
    50% { transform: rotate(-5deg); }
    100% { transform: rotate(5deg); }
}

@keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

</style>
</head>
<body><div class="card">
    <div class="moon"></div>
    <div class="lantern"></div><h1>Selamat Hari Raya</h1>
<p>Maaf Zahir & Batin</p>
<p>Semoga Aidilfitri membawa kebahagiaan, keberkatan dan kemaafan untuk kita semua 🌙✨</p>

</div></body>
</html>